{"tid":1404553,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[多謝post] 琴晚係尖咀肯出車去黃大仙ge的士哥哥真心好感激你","createTime":"2019-08-04T05:07:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T05:07:52.000Z","uid":260570,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c87ec4318cd5b2dd34953921c10ccb79e0eaf7be","tid":1404553,"uid":260570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:07:52.000Z","msg":"[代妹妹出post] [家住wts] <br />\n<br />\n琴晚係尖咀某酒店做完炒散 收到屋企人msg都知尖咀黃大仙都出晒事 諗住搭的士返去 結果我問左10幾架的士聽到黃大仙都話唔去 最後得1架好人的士哥哥肯車<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(我) : 司機去黃大仙<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(的士哥哥): 得上車<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 我問左咁多架 得你肯車 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 我今晚2單 青衣出旺角 再黎旺角出尖咀 唔爭左車埋你去黃大仙啦 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 哇旺角都好危wo睇新聞<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 係呀 去到旺角都比d警察截停左我 我話我開緊工車客囉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 堅勇啊你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 佢地咪又係政府d狗 星期一我都罷工啊 啊妹你洗唔洗返工<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 我都唔返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}